[Term]
id: CL:0000103
name: bipolar neuron
def: "A type of interneuron that has two neurites, usually an axon and a dendrite, extending from opposite poles of an ovoid cell body." [GOC:tfm, ISBN:0444009442]
subset: BDS_subset
subset: cellxgene_subset
