xref: ZFA:0009115 {sssom:mapping_justification="https://w3id.org/semapv/vocab/UnspecifiedMatching"}
is_a: CL:0000255 ! eukaryotic cell
intersection_of: CL:0000000 ! cell
intersection_of: BFO:0000050 UBERON:0001134
