synonym: "RGC" RELATED OMO:0003000 [doi:10.1038/s41598-020-66092-9]
synonym: "RGCs" RELATED OMO:0003004 [doi:10.1038/s41598-020-66092-9]
xref: BTO:0001800
xref: FMA:67765
xref: MESH:D012165
